msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: site/content/en/tutorial.md
msgid ""
"Our [help for developers](https://reuse.software/dev/) lists various "
"resources for programmers like the tool, the API, or how to include checks "
"in CI/CD workflows."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: site/content/en/tutorial.md
msgid ""
"If none of the links above were able to answer your question, please contact "
"us by:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: site/content/en/tutorial.md
msgid ""
"opening an issue on [reuse-website](https://github.com/fsfe/reuse-website) "
"for questions on the tutorial, FAQ or specification;"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: site/content/en/tutorial.md
msgid ""
"opening an issue on [reuse-tool](https://codeberg.org/fsfe/reuse-tool) for "
"questions on the REUSE tool;"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: site/content/en/tutorial.md
msgid ""
"or [sending an email to the FSFE](https://fsfe.org/contact). Please note "
